{"tid":2249162,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想工程轉銀行 求指教","createTime":"2020-10-19T06:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T11:09:49.000Z","uid":35973,"like":8,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"9d79940fd8d784d502bb301c293fd91ed1b17f23","tid":2249162,"uid":35973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"做工程做到好灰... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己本身讀書廢..所以先讀engine 仲要係連登仔口中嘅ASSO後門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢業之後做冷氣裡面maintenance 嘅 Sales Engineer 跟好多個細site ,個個site 有D細微嘅問題都係搵你，次次有鑊都要出現比人鬧, 而老細只會係背後插多你半刀話你係呢單project 嘅負責人無好好管理 blablabla。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工方面個個月都得20k , 13個月糧,無commission <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.日日都做到好灰, 學野又唔多, 又無咩上進心靠牌.<br />\n<br />\n而我家姐同有個friend 都做銀行, 佢地好快就由teller仔上到retail RM <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話曬銀行跑數位都係睇你sell到幾多而出幾多com, 我情願比人捽數都好過係而加係公司日日硬食客嘅鑊氣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過要由而加嘅人工跌返落17k, 挨1年teller 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打門覺得值唔值得轉行 由頭黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf1263a9e64ee8ea3c793d5bad03ec03b0b940e","tid":2249162,"uid":11455,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nfg 都50k啦 垃圾"},{"pid":"529bd3abb05e34a311ee24d9fdee29254d427ff2","tid":224916