":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"做工程做到好灰... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己本身讀書廢..所以先讀engine 仲要係連登仔口中嘅ASSO後門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢業之後做冷氣裡面maintenance 嘅 Sales Engineer 跟好多個細site ,個個site 有D細微嘅問題都係搵你，次次有鑊都要出現比人鬧, 而老細只會係背後插多你半刀話你係呢單project 嘅負責人無好好管理 blablabla。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工方面個個月都得20k , 13個月糧,無commission <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.日日都做到好灰, 學野又唔多, 又無咩上進心靠牌.<br />\n<br />\n而我家姐同有個friend 都做銀行, 佢地好快就由teller仔上到retail RM <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話曬銀行跑數位都係睇你sell到幾多而出幾多com, 我情願比人捽數都好過係而加係公司日日硬食客嘅鑊氣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過要由而加嘅人工跌返落17k, 挨1年teller 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打門覺得值唔值得轉行 由頭黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"咁多人叫你唔好轉行，你就知道工程真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7beb1e03309c9275032d51fb32b2b1c871b6f217","tid":2249162,"uid":35973,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"316b71bcd671dc2ebfc6179780d2436f51a89396","tid":2249162,"uid":57647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"多錢唔洗做銀行啦<br />\n點解唔做保險<br />\n又有數跑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"感覺上銀行狗個名始終好聽過保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n銀行